    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Methods</p>
      <h1>Dry lab &amp; wet lab methodology</h1>
      <p>
        Complete protocols for both the computational structural analysis and the molecular
        biology experiments. Every method links directly to the relevant results.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

